<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Payout Request Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #dddddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #016ec0;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777777;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #016ec0;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <img src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/samukele-8fd68.appspot.com/o/classifieds%2FST%20LOGO%20HORIZONTAL%20BLACK%20NO%20BG.png?alt=media&token=ffeb3078-55d2-4359-8a45-bb7ce27fe794" alt="Logo" style="display: block; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px 0;" width="200">

    <div class="header">
      <h1>Payout Request Received</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi {{seller_name}},</p>
      <p>We've received your payout request of <strong>R{{amount}}</strong>.</p>
      <p>Your funds will be deposited into your account within the next <strong>3 business days</strong>.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us at <a
          href="mailto:support@schoolthrifties.co.za">support@schoolthrifties.co.za</a>.</p>
          <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{website_url}}" class="button">View Your Payouts</a>
          </div>
      <br>
      <br>
      <small>Questions or suggestions? Please feel free to reply to this email and we will get back to you as soon as possible. ðŸ˜Š</small>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} School Thrifties. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>